{"about_the_game":"Dracula Awakens is a short horror game about Dracula's return to this world.<br><br>A world where you desperately need to keep your job. And to do so, you offer to get evidence about the disappearance of a man in Dracula's castle, which was a tourist attraction before the incident.<br><br>Since the police didn't care about the immigrant man, <strong>you</strong> will find out what happened to him.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Welcome to Dracula's Castle</h2></h2><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2634470/extras/gif4_door_.gif?t=1735684730\" /><br><br>Here you will find:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>An ancient vampire lord with his wife chasing you<br></li><li>Retro style low poly graphics<br></li><li>Unique puzzles<br></li><li>A castle and catacombs to explore<br></li><li>Bats and ghosts to use your super flash camera<br></li><li>Multiple endings<br></li><li>Manual save in the save room (no newbie-friendly autosave)</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Gameplay</h2><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2634470/extras/gif_1_GhostChaser_.gif?t=1735684730\" /><br><br>Simple and effective as it looks: A camera with a super flash ready to aim and shoot, enemies and your limited medicine to heal if you are surprised from behind.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2634470/extras/gif2_heal_.gif?t=1735684730\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">The Castle</h2><br>Solve unique puzzles and explore the castle while surviving.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2634470/extras/gif3_puzzle_solve_.gif?t=1735684730\" /><br><br>Please note: This game is an experience that can be completed in under 2 hours and is aimed at players who enjoy old school survival horror games.","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Exc